;; TEST-ID: tests.codegen.rt-begin-variants
;; TEST-CONTEXT: monadc.context.language.runtime-codegen-corpus
;; TEST-PURPOSE: Runtime begin forms return the last expression or nil-like zero for empty begin.
;; TEST-ATOM: Empty, single-expression, and nested begin forms compile and run.
